<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٥٣ - طُولُ اللِّحْيَةِ دَلِيلُ <span class="c4">[قِلَّةِ]</span> الْعَقْلِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>لَا يُعْرَفُ بِهَذَا وَعِنْدَ الدَّيْلَمِيِّ حَدِيثُ عَمْرِو بْنِ الْعَاصِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٢٥٤ - اعْتَبِرُوا عَقْلَ الرَّجُلِ فِي ثَلاثٍ فِي طُولِ لِحْيَتِهِ وَكُنْيَتِهِ وَنَقْشِ خَاتَمِهِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَهُوَ وَاهٍ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٢٥٥ - طَيُّ الْقُمَاشِ يَزِيدُ فِي زِيِّهِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>لَا يُعْرَفُ لَكِنْ أَخْرَجَ الدَّيْلَمِيُّ عَنْ جَابِرٍ حَدِيثَ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٢٥٦ - طَيُّ الثَّوْبِ رَاحَتُهُ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَالطَّبَرَانِيُّ عَنْهُ حَدِيثُ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>